          "reviewBody": "Eurokids Lohegaon is amazing preschool and day care in Lohegaon area. Wonderful study environment, well trained teachers, supportive non teaching staff, well equipped classroom , I am satisfied for my daughter being in such school and day care.\nI was worried about my daughter as she is below 2 years but now I got great preschool and day care with cctv access.\n\nMe and my husband in search for good preschool and daycare in lohegaon pune and we had visited this center where we found both the facilities also the staff and attention found in this centers is up to mark.\n\nHighly recommended to everyone.",
