            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "1st stage performance of my Son praneet samal ❤️....I would like 2 take this opportunity to congratulate the whole school for an amazing and extraordinary Annual Day program held on 12thMarch 2023.\nThe show was spectacular, especially the theme- “Echo on Earth”. It was great to see the enthusiasm and hard work in all the acts of all students and teachers specially  and how well the theme was depicted in the form of drama and dance.\n\nWorking in a office is easy but to work in a preschool with all the toddlers are quite difficult task 😀😀Anyways thanks to Yogita Kage Gaikwad mam, Nikita mam,Naznee mam, Aarti Jamwal n d entire team❣️❣️their dedication towards our children r always 🙏🙏🫶🫶\n\nIt is live witness that from all the branches, VN team always rocking, majority wise, participation wise... also VN team, active teachers wise also team Viman Nagar rocks❣️❣️❣️love for all.\n\nRegards\nPranati\nMother of Praneet Samal\nPre k student of Viman nagar branch, mindseed",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
