            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My daughter has recently joined Mindseed (Vimannagar)as a toddler and we can already see a lot of positive changes in her behavior. She has become more independent, confident, improved motor skills and much more. Recently she even participated in the annual day and gave her first stage performance. We were pleasantly shocked to see her own the stage confidently. It did not seem like her first stage performance at all. We would like to thank all the teachers and maushis and who ensure that she learns and grows well. We are liking all these changes and excited in seeing whats up for the future.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
